{"tid":14684,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"做咗咁多人未dem過beat，係咪遺憾","createTime":"2016-11-30T15:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T15:53:04.000Z","uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e473f589c3aef27673a0182af32f027f682cfa","tid":14684,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"今晚收咗工如常地自己一個食飯，<br />\n見凍凍地就心血來潮想食煲仔飯，<br />\n見附近咁啱有間就毫不猶豫坐低咗。<br />\n等緊個飯開蓋嗰陣，<br />\n百無聊賴，<br />\n望到對面檯學生哥圍住坐，<br />\n臨食飯前拍哂檯咁喺到dembeat，<br />\n好齊心，好熱血，<br />\n同時我亦覺得好唏噓。<br />\n到底我讀U嗰幾年喺到做咩呢，<br />\n打開電話掃吓個contact list，<br />\n已經分唔清邊啲係中學同學，<br />\n邊啲係大學同學。<br />\n放低電話，<br />\n拎起杯藍妹，<br />\n三十而立，我究竟喺到做乜嘢。"},{"pid":"b499dff4e7d3a66ffa7ce2f9a8fe4ca8126452eb","tid":14684,"uid":23544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:47:24.000Z","msg":"未讀過u留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bbd681867a4561cf13cdb4700fe648dcd51afd","tid":14684,"uid":5077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未讀過u留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我願意用張cert嚟交換幾個真心好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}